# Goal
# Cap on total shoulder-pan rotation (rad) used to bias the arm away from the
# obstacle (prevents large/unsafe swings). <= 0 disables the pan bias.
float32 max_pan_change
# Maximum time allowed for the maneuver.
builtin_interfaces/Duration time_allowance
---
# Result
builtin_interfaces/Duration total_elapsed_time
---
# Feedback
float32 footprint_cost
